sentences: Graciela Agudelo (December 7, 1945 â€“ April 19, 2018) was a Mexican pianist and composer.
She received a scholarship from the Internationales Musikinstitu Darmstadt in Germany.
She is the author of the Musical Initiation GAM Method for Children (ENM / UNAM, 1998) and Man and Music (Patria, 1998).
In 2002 she received the Xochipilli award for outstanding creativity in the field of music in Mexico.
